All code was written by Jon Link*

*EXCEPT some parts of code found in game_display.php 
those snippets are from phpChessBoard by Andreas Stieger 
(phpChessBoard is gone as far as I can tell)

*EXCEPT the user input validation function is a 
modification of a function found on http://php.net

*EXCEPT major portions of the backup script are taken from
http://www.lunarforums.com/forum/index.php?topic=22118.0

*EXCEPT CSS code to make rounded boxes
http://www.cssplay.co.uk/boxes/snazzy.html

